<ab facs="#facs_199_r2l8">des <expan>vorgen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> Hercʒog Fridrichs land vnd gepıete mit
